summary:
Complete 360-degree audit of the Wealth Aggregator v1.1 application covering:
- Executive summary with overall 4/5 star rating
- 7 critical/medium bugs identified (API key exposure, @ts-ignore, memory leaks, etc.)
- Architecture analysis with scalability scores
- Deep dive into all 12+ tabs with current state, issues, and improvements
- 30+ god-tier feature recommendations across 5 categories
- Prioritized 10-week roadmap
- Competitive analysis vs Groww, INDMoney, MoneyControl
- Final verdict with actionable next steps
